QuestData.Title: Owl Soul
QuestData.Description: <The Owl Soul is solemn and smart. The shape of the owl will be yours to call upon.>
QuestData.LogDescription: Bring the Owl Soul to Lady Muunn in the Heart of the Forest.
QuestData.QuestCompletionLog: Bring the Owl Soul to Lady Muunn in the Heart of the Forest.
QuestData.RewardText: Ah, the owl. This shape is now yours to call upon.
